critical_positive: We were both very nice and open people, willing to do whatever it took to complete our assignment. I think we were pleasantly surprised that we were both pleasant people and shared the same political beliefs. We were both ok with using some light humor and looked for our commonalities right away, which helped anchor the conversation.
critical_negative: There was some sadness and weirdness when our conversation touched on some of the unfair differences in our lives, namely the economic pressures my partner faces.
